    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 11th level, your @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.gaVd6MJT8Q6PLE9B]{Rage} can keep you fighting despite grievous wounds.</p>\n<p>If you drop to 0 hit points while you're raging and don't die outright, you can make a DC 10 <strong>Constitution saving throw</strong>. If you succeed, you drop to 1 hit point instead.</p>\n<p>Each time you use this feature after the first, the DC increases by 5. When you finish a <strong>short </strong>or <strong>long rest</strong>, the DC resets to 10.</p>",
